<SYNC Start=2628971><P Class=KNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2630885><P Class=KNCC>
네?
<SYNC Start=2632819><P Class=KNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2632887><P Class=KNCC>
