<SYNC Start=5287981><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5288054><P Class=KRCC>
친애하는, 내 사랑 미란다
<SYNC Start=5292047><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5302335><P Class=KRCC>
